      "post_content": "The duel use of this is two cards in 1.  \n  \nA better version of [Mantle of Leadership](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mantle of Leadership) to buff your creatures if you have them. Or to cast a [Pacifism](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pacifism) if your opponent has the bigger threat. What's not to love about that kind of versatility for 2 mana?  \n  \nPro Tip: Play in a humans theme deck. Nice artwork on the card.  \n  \n  ",
